title: 2009 Arab Athletics Championships
text: The 2009 <a href="Arab%20Athletics%20Championships">Arab Athletics Championships</a> was the sixteenth edition of the international <a href="athletics%20%28sport%29">athletics</a> competition between <a href="Arab%20countries">Arab countries</a> which took place in <a href="Damascus">Damascus</a>, Syria from 6–9 October.
